Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看到我吗\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:10.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能听到我吗\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是怎么发生的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:14.71,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我与你之间可能隔着千山万水\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I could be thousands of miles away,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:17.17,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 只要你打开你的设备\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and yet, when you turn on whatever device
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:19.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的声音和图像就会传到你那里\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is bringing my image and voice to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.15,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就在这里\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:22.91,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会有任何的间断\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Instantaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:25.15,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这一切是如何变成现实的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:27.22,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对于我们的祖先来说\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To our ancestors,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:29.15,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这一切看起来就像是魔法\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it would've seemed like sorcery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:31.39,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对他们来说,信息传播的速度\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For them, speed of communication
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:33.49,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}取决于快马的速度\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}was only as fast as the swiftest horse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:35.59,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或是航船的速度\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or sailing ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:39.43,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现代社会的信息以肉眼不可见的光速进行传播\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our messages travel invisibly at the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:42.27,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们是如何获得如此不可思议的力量的呢\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How did we attain such mythic powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:45.27,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这一切都来源于一个人的头脑\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It all began in the mind of one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:47.61,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个贫民家的小孩\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A child of poverty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:50.61,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听起来没什么可期待的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of whom nothing was expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:57.25,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可要是没有这个人\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In fact, if this man had not lived...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:04.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们现在的世界也许就不会是这个样子\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the world we know might not exist today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:42.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\fe134}{\fsp0}{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(190,278)}{\fn方正准圆简体}{\bord0}{\fs20}{\c&H24EFFF&}宇宙大探索\N{\fs17}{\c&HFFFFFF&} 第十集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.96,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许迟早有那么一天\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sooner or later,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总有人能作出\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}someone would've likely figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:53.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他的某些发现\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}some of his discoveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:56.23,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但如果迈克尔・法拉第没有在这世界上出现过\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But if Michael Faraday had never lived,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:03:00.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们现在可能还活在和十七世纪的人们一样的世界里\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we might still be living as our ancestors did in the 17th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根本不会意识到\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Unaware
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:05.64,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的身边有着看不见的力量等待着我们的使唤\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of armies of invisible servants awaiting our commands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:08.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是关于我们如何掌握了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is the story of how we learned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:11.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电的力量的故事\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to make electrons do our bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:16.39,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从某个方面来说 这一切始于一位伟大的天才人物\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In a way, it begins with the greatest genius who ever lived--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.42,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾萨克・牛顿\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Isaac Newton.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:27.26,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里是牛顿的故居 伍尔斯索普\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is Woolsthorpe, Newton's ancestral home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:27.26,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}位于英国  1642年12月25日 牛顿在此出生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:30.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他在这条小路上总是在那苦苦思索着\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He walked these fields, tormented by mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.94,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}牛顿 正是他发现了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Newton, the man who figured out the formula
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行星绕日运动的规律\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for the motions of the planets around the Sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.71,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他还想知道\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}wanted to know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:39.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太阳是如何让行星围绕着它旋转\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how does the Sun make the planets act that way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:41.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而又不用互相接触\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}without touching them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:43.55,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}树上的苹果怎么知道何时该掉落\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How do all the apples know how to fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:46.55,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}另一位天才同样从另一个方面\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Another genius was puzzled by another aspect
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:49.12,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被这个问题所困扰\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the same mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}儿子 看哪\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You see, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:01.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无论我怎样转动这个指南针\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No matter how I turn the compass,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:05.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}针头总会指向相同的方向\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the needle always points the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.50,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除非...\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:14.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会呢\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们根本就没碰到\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They do not touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:20.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔伯特 我还没听到你说'谢谢'\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I didn't hear a "Thank you," Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我依然记得这个故事\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I can still remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:29.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它们给了我深深的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The experience made a deep
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.86,0:04:32.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}连绵不绝的感动\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and lasting impression on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.87,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定有某些东西深深地隐藏在\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Something deeply hidden
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:38.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这一切的背后\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}had to be behind things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:41.17,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在爱因斯坦与牛顿之间\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Between the lifetimes of Einstein and Newton,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还出现了另一位天才\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there lived another genius,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}与他们同样伟大\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one of equal stature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:48.85,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这位天才解决了困扰牛顿的问题\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The man who solved the mystery that stumped Newton,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:53.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也奠定了爱因斯坦的革命性发现的基础\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}also laid the foundation for Einstein's revolutionary insights.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:56.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及人类今天生存的方式\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And for the way we live now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:20.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1791年 在伦敦郊区的一个脏兮兮的贫民窟里\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In 1791, in a squalid slum in the suburbs of London,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迈克尔・法拉第出生了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Michael Faraday was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:31.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在学校里 他显示不出一丁点的天分\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He showed little promise at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.09,0:05:38.43,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请告诉我们一个\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Pray tell us a word that begins
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:40.43,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以字母R开头的单词\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with the letter R.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:42.43,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.60,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肚子\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:49.07,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}应该是「兔子」\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The word is "Rabbit."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:52.61,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再来一次 这次发音要准啊\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Once again, and correctly this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肚子\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Wabbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:56.81,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在嘲弄我吗\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do you mock me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.72,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道我没有告诉你\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Have I not told you how
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么去念R这个字母的发音吗\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to pronounce the letter R?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:03.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但起码你能告诉我们你的名字吧\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Surely you can at least tell us your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:07.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迈克尔・法老地 老师\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Michael "Fawaday," ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿这半个便士\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Take this ha'penny,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:11.60,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}买根鞭回来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and buy me a cane,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:14.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看我怎么给你那无礼的弟弟抽一顿\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so that I may give your insolent brother a proper flogging.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}史书上再也没有任何法拉弟\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}History does not record that Michael Faraday
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:36.29,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去学校读书的记载\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ever attended school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:42.63,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉第承传了家庭的正统基督教信仰\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday took his family's fundamentalist Christian faith
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.20,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他的虔诚\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是他强大的精神动力源泉\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would always remain a source of strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让他平和而谦逊\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}comfort and humility for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:52.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}13岁时他被送到一个书籍装订厂工作\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He was sent to work at a bookbindery at the age of 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:55.47,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白天 他在装订书籍\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By day, he bound the books,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:56.64,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了晚上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and by night,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.81,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他在读书\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:01.21,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是他终生\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It was the beginning of a lifelong fascination
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:01.21,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}《电的历史与现前状态》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:04.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为电而痴狂的起始\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:20.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在书籍装订厂里工作了有些年头以后\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}After years of working in the bookbindery,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:22.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}21岁的法拉弟\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday, now 21,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.74,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}渴望来到一个更广阔的世界\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}yearned to escape to a larger world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他的机会来了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}His big break came
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.64,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一位顾客给了他一张门票\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when a customer gave him a ticket
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让他去参加一项挺受欢迎的新休闲活动――\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to a sensational new kind of entertainment--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:33.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公众科普讲座\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}science for the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:40.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正是在这里\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it started right here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伦敦皇家学院\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at London's Royal Institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}汉弗莱・戴维不仅仅是\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Humphry Davy was not only
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:47.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当时首屈一指的科学家\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one of the leading scientists of his day,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他也发现了好几种化学元素\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he discovered several chemical elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}包括钙和钠\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}including calcium and sodium.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.17,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他同时也是一位出色的主持人\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He was also a consummate showman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:57.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对于电学原理的初步演示\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And primitive demonstrations of electricity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深受公众的欢迎\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}never failed as a crowd pleaser.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:04.28,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请把灯光调暗 好吗\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}May we have the lights lowered, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我现在就要释放出\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I am about to unleash the might
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.61,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}两千块化学电池的能量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the 2,000 massive chemical batteries
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:15.05,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它们就在我们脚下的地下室里\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}stored in the cellar beneath our feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:21.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在 就是见证神秘的力量的时刻\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And now, behold the power of the mysterious force
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:26.63,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它来自于电解液 它将照耀我们的未来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of electrical fluid to illuminate our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:48.92,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉第忙着做笔记 根本无暇鼓掌\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday was too busy taking notes to applaud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:55.66,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉利创作了一份戴维演讲的记录\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday created a transcript of Davy's lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:58.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他把做学徒时学得的技巧都用上了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Using the skills he had learned as an apprentice,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:01.40,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他把这些都放在了这本书里\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he bound them into this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:05.07,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许正是这样的才能\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Perhaps such a gift would bring him to the attention
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.10,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让他得到了这位伟人的注意\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:17.98,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许这一切举动是奔往\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Maybe this gesture could be a means of escape
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:20.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更广阔世界的方式\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to a much larger universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早上好 先生\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Good day, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:32.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请帮我把这个包裹交给汉弗莱爵士\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I wish you to deliver this parcel to Sir Humphry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:41.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎么说 这就像一个赌注\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It was a long shot, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.98,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉利希望能赌中些什么\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But Faraday hoped something would come of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:47.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结果他真的赌中了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:53.25,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呃 实验已经准备好了 先生\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Uh, the experiment is ready for you now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:02.16,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安培告诉我说可怜的杜隆\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ampere tells me that poor Dulong lost an eye
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:04.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在做这个实验时 丢掉了一只眼睛和三个手指\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and three fingers working with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.84,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的眼睛\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:13.10,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的眼睛\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:26.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当一场化学实验\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When a chemical experiment blew up in the face
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:29.18,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把知名科学家汉弗莱戴维的脸弄伤之后\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the world-renowned scientist Humphry Davy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:31.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他想起了法拉弟\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he remembered Michael Faraday,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.55,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个小伙子能一大段一大段地\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the lad who had gone through such lengths
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:37.85,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把他的讲座记录并整理下来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to copy down and bind the transcript of his lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:40.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}年轻人 你真是记忆力超群\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You have a first-rate memory, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:42.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我正好暂时需要一个秘书\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And I shall have temporary need of a secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:46.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先生 我做梦都想着为科学服务\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sir, I dream of a life in service to science.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:49.50,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我建议你还是继续做好你这份书籍装订的工作\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I would advise you to stick to the bookbinding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:52.03,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}科学研究残酷而无情\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Science is a harsh mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.87,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了 像你这样的地位 人又谦虚\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Surely, a person of your station and modest means
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.20,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}应当有自己的生意吧\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}must have a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:58.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做生意的人狠毒而自私\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Trade is vicious and selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:02.21,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做科学研究的人和蔼而品格高尚\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Men of science are amiable and morally superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.24,0:11:05.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很好 我就是你在科学界里\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I take it I'm the first man of science
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:06.45,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第一位遇到的人\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:12.95,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉利最终成为戴维身边不可或缺的人物\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday made himself indispensable to Davy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:15.39,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这份临时的工作成为他终身的职业\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The temporary job became a permanent one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:18.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}英国皇家学会成为他生命的归宿\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the Royal Institution became his lifelong home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:21.76,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白天 他在实验室协助戴维\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By day, he assisted Davy in the lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:25.03,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚上 他就走到楼上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at day's end, he climbed the stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:26.63,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回到他那小小的蜗居\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to the little apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:29.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他亲爱的妻子莎拉在等待着他\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where his beloved bride Sarah was waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:39.91,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}汉弗莱・戴维与化学家威廉・瓦尔森\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Humphry Davy and the chemist William Wollaston
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:47.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在实验中遇到了和两个保持距离的物品相关的一个神奇的现象\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}were experimenting with a mysterious phenomenon, one with potentially far-reaching implications.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:50.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个装置和丹麦科学家奥斯特的试验相似\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is the identical setup to Orsted's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:54.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在把线圈闭合 戴维 仔细盯着\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now close the circuit, Davy, and watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:00.63,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是什么东西让针偏离了电线\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What could be driving the needle away from the wire?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:03.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道就好了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Damned if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:04.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过看上去似乎是通电的线圈\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But it's as if the electric current
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让电线有了类似磁铁的力量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}makes the wire behave like some kind of magnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:10.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电流一定具有某种磁力\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Electricity must have something to do with magnetism.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:15.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我们能让它不断地运转就好了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now if we could only get it to turn continuously,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想象一下 如果我们能掌握了这些力量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}imagine what might be accomplished
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.76,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}世界将会有怎样的变化\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if we could put these forces to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:25.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把东西整理好后 法拉弟\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}After you tidy up, Faraday,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.06,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许你可以试试你能做点什么\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you might see what you can make of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:31.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戴维也许只是开个小玩笑\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Davy may have been having a bit of fun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:32.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘲弄一下他的年轻助手\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at the expense of his young assistant,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:35.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但法拉弟的心中燃起了激情\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but Faraday was on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:38.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当时 电还只能被用做\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Up to now, electricity had been nothing more
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:40.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用来娱乐大众的新奇玩意\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than an entertaining novelty toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:43.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它被用来创造闪光\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It could make a light flash for an instant
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或是让指南针转个弯\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or turn a compass needle briefly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:48.48,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但没有什么实际的用途\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it had no practical application.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:52.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉弟立即着手设计实验\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday immediately set about designing the experiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.69,0:12:56.56,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把他闲暇的每一刻都用在解决这个问题上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}devoting every moment of his spare time to the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.76,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果法拉弟成功了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If Faraday succeeded,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.79,0:13:02.16,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他就能把无尽的 隐秘的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he would be putting an infinitely large, invisible,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:05.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不为人知的电子的力量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and as-yet-undiscovered army of electrons
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:09.27,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}化为人类所用\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at the command of human whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:12.84,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个革命是如果何开始的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How does a revolution begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:16.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实也不用花费太多\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sometimes it doesn't take much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:19.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一块金属 一碗水银\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A piece of metal, a bowl of mercury,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一点黄柏\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a bit of cork.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.25,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲爱的莎拉 把你的小弟叫下来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sarah dear, send your little brother down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.26,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就要开始做个新实验了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm about to try something knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:30.69,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想让他看看\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and I want him to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:33.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乔治 由你来开启这光荣时刻吧\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why don't you do the honors, Georgie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:39.53,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它动起来了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There she goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:41.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它动起来了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There she goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:52.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是人类的第一台马达\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This was the first motor
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:56.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它能把电流转化为无间断的机械运动\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}converting electric current into continuous mechanical motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.99,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看上去弱爆了 是不是\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Looks pretty feeble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:01.26,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可就是这转动中的小纺锤\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But that turning spindle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:04.09,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开启了一场革命\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the beginning of a revolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:06.56,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一件微小的发明引爆了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one that dwarfs all the shots fired
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.63,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一连串的连锁反应\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and bombs ever detonated
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:13.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对人类文明产生了庞大的影响\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the sheer magnitude of its effect on our civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:17.10,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想象一下 我们现在的商业\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Try to imagine all the businesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:19.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}工业 科技\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}industries, technologies,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.48,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们生活中的种种变化\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}transformations of the way we live
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:24.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都源于这欢乐的一刻\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that have their beginnings in that ecstatic moment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:27.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}源于法拉弟的实验室\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in Michael Faraday's laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:30.25,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉弟的新发明的新闻很快传了出去\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}News of Faraday's invention spread quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:35.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一夜之间 戴维的助手成为伦敦的热门人物\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and suddenly, Davy's assistant was the toast of London.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:37.53,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戴维很不爽\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Davy didn't take it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:41.03,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}毕竟 他曾发现了好些个元素\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He had, after all, discovered all those elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:46.53,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可现在人们都在说 他最大的发现\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now people were saying that his greatest discovery
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:49.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是发现了法拉弟\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}was Michael Faraday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:51.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戴维要确保法拉弟\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Davy made sure that Faraday
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:55.98,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很快不再成为新闻\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}wouldn't be making any more headlines anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:14:59.98,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您找我吗 先生\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You sent for me, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:02.22,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有个新任务要交给你\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I have a new challenge for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.72,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想要你去接下\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I want you to take over our efforts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:08.59,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}改进英国光学镜片质量的任务\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to improve the quality of British optical glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:12.96,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些该死的巴伐利亚人把我们的市场都占领了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Those damned Bavarians are running circles around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.03,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}镜片\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:15.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请恕我冒昧 先生\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}With all due respect, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:18.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我对镜片制造一无所知啊\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I know nothing at all of glass-making.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.50,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就好好学吧 法拉弟\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then you will learn, Faraday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:23.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正你学什么都很快\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We all know what a quick study you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:26.57,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你只需要分析那些镜片的化学成分\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just analyze the chemical composition of their glass
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再逆向找出它的制造过程\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and work backwards to see how they made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这不会花很长时间的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It shouldn't take you long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:40.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可法拉弟苦苦花了4年时间\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But Faraday struggled for four years
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.39,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}依然一无所获\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}without any success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:01.41,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这次比上一次更糟糕\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is even worse than the last batch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:04.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管他如何努力\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No matter how hard he tried,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:10.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉弟始终没能找到约瑟夫?弗劳恩霍夫在数年前的发现\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday could not figure out what Joseph Fraunhofer had discovered years before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:14.39,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉弟失败在于他没能掌握生产\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What Faraday failed to grasp was that casting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:19.36,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完美的光学镜片的技术与科学原理\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}perfect optical glass for telescopes was a craft as well as a science, and the masters
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:22.26,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些技术的秘密被巴伐利亚的大师们完好的隐藏起来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in Bavaria kept their secrets under lock and key.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:32.74,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉利没能掌握这些秘密\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday never did learn their secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:35.21,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他把一块玻璃砖保存了下来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He kept a single glass brick
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:38.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}作为失败的纪念品\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as a souvenir of this failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:43.48,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几年后 这块东西同样改变了他的生活\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Years later, it would change the course of his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.69,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有我们的生活\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:09.27,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戴维的去世最终结束了这项无果的项目\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Davy's death finally brought an end to this fruitless project,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:12.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而法拉弟 这个贫民窟的孩子\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and Faraday, the boy from the slums,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:14.81,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成为了实验室的主管\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}succeeded him as Director of the Laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:18.48,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉弟利用他的权力做出了一些史无前例的事情\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday used his new authority to do something unprecedented--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.52,0:17:21.25,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他从1825年开始举办了一系列专门为\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a series of annual Christmas lectures on science
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:24.52,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}青少年而设的圣诞节年度科普讲座\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for the young... beginning in 1825
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.16,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并一直延续到了现在\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and continuing to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:32.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}尽管皇家学院的听课费颇为昂贵 但只要是法拉第讲演 讲座厅就会挤得水泄不通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:35.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}其它人的讲座平均只有三分之二的听众
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:40.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}某次的圣诞节讲座的主题为《蜡烛的化学史》 被翻译成各种语言 至今仍在出版
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:45.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}1846年法拉第在皇家学院代替查理・惠斯通作一次报告 当时惠斯通原定报告他的一些研究工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:50.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}但到了最后一刻他突然惊慌失措爬出会场 法拉第只好作了一个即场演讲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:58.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}法拉第所作的这些演讲 在不久之后却扮演了将科学推广到社会的重要角色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在某个首次举办的圣诞节讲座上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At one of the first Christmas lectures,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:03.36,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉利让他的听众们着迷\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday enchanted his audience
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:07.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他展示了他所掌握的新能量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with displays of the new powers that were at his disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:11.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}假设我要点着这堆火药\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Suppose I want to fire a portion of gunpowder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很轻松的就可以 通过\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I can readily do it with the power
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电的力量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:22.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我通过这根电缆让电流经过我的身体\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If I receive electricity through this conducting wire,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.11,0:18:24.42,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我就能把电导到我接触的作任何物体上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I can then give it to anything I touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:28.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过我得先站到这张有玻璃绝缘腿的凳子上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But I must stand on these insulating glass leg
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:31.92,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不然电流就会跑到地板上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to prevent the electricity from going away into the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:37.53,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在 我通电了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now I am electrified!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:39.23,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:46.60,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就靠我这根手指\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do you think I could light this gas jet
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.87,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能点着这盏汽灯么\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just by touching it with my finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:50.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 不要啊\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, don't do it! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:52.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 不要\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:57.72,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小朋友在家里不要学 叔叔有练过的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, mind you, don't try this at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:05.29,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在 孩子们 用你们的眼睛看吧\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And now, my children, you have seen for yourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:07.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是看不见的电的力量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how this invisible force of electricity
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:10.29,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它能为我们做更多的事\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}can be made to serve new purposes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:13.90,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但以我们目前的力量还不能完全做到\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}utterly unattainable by the powers we have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:26.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马达的发明\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The invention of a motor that could work continuously,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:26.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}港译 摩达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:29.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能让人类从劳苦的工作中释放出来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}eliminating countless human hours of drudgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:32.05,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能让人类更加富裕\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would be more than enough to make you a fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.05,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也能让人永载史册\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and land you in the history books.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但法拉弟没有看到这些\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But that's not how Michael Faraday saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:39.82,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他从来没有申请专利的念头\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He had absolutely no interest in patenting his ideas
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也没想过从中获私利\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or personally profiting from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至于史书\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And as for the history books,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:46.06,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他仅仅写下第一行字\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he had only written the first sentence
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}后面的许多篇章都来不及了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of an entry that would be many pages long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:53.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安德森先生 请把灯光调暗吧\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mr. Anderson, may I ask you to dim the lights, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:57.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先生们 只需动一动这块磁铁\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Gentlemen, I am about to induce a current of electricity
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:59.18,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就可以制造出电流\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}merely by moving a magnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请好好观察吧\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Please observe what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:03.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我这样做的时候 请好好看着线圈的间隙\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the gap between the wires when I do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:13.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们看到了磁铁在运行时电流是如何流动的吗\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Do you see how the current only flows when the magnet is moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:16.76,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是将\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is the conversion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.90,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}动能转为化为电能\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of motion into electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是人类第一台发电机\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This was the first generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.71,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从此 电能被人类掌控\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}From here, electricity would become available on demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:39.32,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉弟在不断地改变着世界以及人类的生活\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday was continuing to change the world and the way people lived,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.39,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而 天嫉英才\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:44.76,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}病魔侵袭了他那举世无双的大脑\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}an illness attacked his incomparable mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:52.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲爱的舍恩拜\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My dear Schoenbein,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.33,0:20:55.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很高兴看到你的观点 我认为…\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I would be very grateful to have your opinion regarding...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.71,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我认为…\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Regarding...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:07.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲爱的舍恩拜…我认为…\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dear Schoenbein... Regarding...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:20.59,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老公 怎么了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My dear husband, whatever is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:23.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想写封信给舍恩拜\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I began a letter to Schoenbein
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:26.26,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可就是记不得我想要写什么了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and could not remember what I meant to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:28.50,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别担心\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is no cause for alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:30.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你工作太累了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You work too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:32.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-已经精疲力尽了 -不是的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- You're exhausted. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:33.84,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}莎拉 这次不一样\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sarah, this is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.84,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的很不一样\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Horribly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:39.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的大脑出现这样的问题很多天了 这是第三次了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's the third time my memory has failed me in as many days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:41.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只怕我要失去我的记忆力了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I fear I'm losing my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:43.82,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我该如何是好\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And what would I be without that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.48,0:21:50.09,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老公 别担心 会好的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Why, my darling husband, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:53.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉弟49岁时\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When Faraday was 49,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.89,0:21:56.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他便开始面临失忆与抑郁症的困扰\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he began to battle severe memory loss and depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:59.40,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这使得他的工作陷入了停顿\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}His work came to a standstill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:01.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然他从此没有完全康复过\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And although he never fully recovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:05.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但他更大的发现还在后头\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}his greatest achievements still lay ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:24.63,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉弟完全地沉浸在电力与磁力的实验中\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday had immersed himself so deeply in electrical and magnetic experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:27.50,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他观察到磁铁的周围\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that he came to visualize the space around a magnet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:31.20,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有看不见的力场线\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as filled with invisible lines of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:34.64,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}磁铁不仅仅是一块磁化的小铁块\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A magnet was not simply the magnetized bar of iron
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:36.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不仅仅是肉眼所见的一切\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that you could see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:38.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有某些我们看不见的东西\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It was also the unseen something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:41.45,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}围绕着磁铁四周的空间\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the space around the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.48,0:22:43.95,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他称之为场\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that something he called a field.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:47.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是磁场\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:50.06,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉弟认为在自然界这个统一的整体中\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday believed in the unity of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:52.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无处不在展示着\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Having demonstrated the connections
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:56.23,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电场与磁场的关连\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}between electricity and magnetism, he wondered,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.26,0:23:00.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这两者会不会与第三种能量――光 相关连\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}were these two forces also connected to a third-- light?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:03.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果他能展示出\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If he could only show a connection
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.27,0:23:06.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这三种不可见现象之间的关连\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}among these three invisible phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:08.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么自然界最隐秘的奥秘之一\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one of nature's most intimate secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:10.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就会被人类揭开\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would at last be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.54,0:23:12.55,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最终 他是怎么做的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, what did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:14.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他设计了一项试验\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He designed an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:17.42,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉弟知道光能像波一样传播\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday knew that light can travel as a wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.45,0:23:20.49,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}光波在各个方向随机振动\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Waves of light vibrate randomly in all directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:24.09,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但有个方法可以固定某个特定的光波\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But there's a way to isolate a single wave of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:27.09,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个方法就是偏振\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's called polarization.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:28.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当光从反射面反弹回来时\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When light bounces off a reflective surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.86,0:23:30.26,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比如一面镜子\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like a mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:32.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就会出现偏振\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it becomes polarized.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.87,0:23:34.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉弟想知道\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday wanted to see
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:37.84,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一条单束的光线是否能被\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if that single ray of light could be manipulated
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.87,0:23:39.87,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可见的磁场所控制\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by the invisible magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:42.41,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这块目镜含有水晶\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The eyepiece contained a crystal
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:45.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它就如同一道栅栏挡住了光线\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that acted as a kind of picket fence for light.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.41,0:23:47.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果光线想要穿过它\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Light could only pass through it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:49.85,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就必须受磁场的影响而偏移\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if it was somehow moved by the magnet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:52.05,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他在镜子前面放了一盏灯\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He placed a lantern before a mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.09,0:23:55.26,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果他能通过目镜看到灯光\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}one that he would only see through the eyepiece
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.29,0:23:58.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那说明反射光穿过了栅栏\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if its reflection could pass through the picket fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.93,0:24:02.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你觉得很难理解 这很正常\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If this is hard to understand, don't feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.16,0:24:04.06,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这之后的100年里\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scientists could not explain this phenomenon
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.10,0:24:05.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}科学家们也不能解释这种现象\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for another 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.80,0:24:08.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉利知道磁场\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday knew that magnetism had no effect
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:11.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对空气中移动的光线没有任何影响\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on light that was moving through air.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:14.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可要是光线在其它物体中移动呢\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But what about when it was moving through other materials?
