Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.08,0:24:21.15,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他测试了好几百种\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He tried hundreds of different
