Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.46,0:24:35.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}碳酸钠\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}sodium carbonate,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.50,0:24:37.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}硫酸钙\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}calcium sulfate,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.37,0:24:39.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可还是什么都看不见\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and still, he saw nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.00,0:24:41.74,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他测试了好几种酸\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He tried acids.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.77,0:24:42.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}硫酸\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sulfuric acid,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.84,0:24:44.64,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}盐酸\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}muriatic acid,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.67,0:24:46.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}碳酸\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}carbonic acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.71,0:24:48.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有气体…\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He tried gasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.18,0:24:51.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}氧气 氮气 氢气…\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}oxygen, nitrogen, hydrogen...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.11,0:24:52.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}均以失败告终\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with no success.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.78,0:24:55.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}受这些物质所感应的磁场\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The magnetic field induced
