Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.72,0:24:59.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让他看到油灯的灯光\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from his lamp back into view.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.02,0:25:02.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}见鬼了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.56,0:25:12.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无奈之下 他决定要试一试\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In desperation, he decided to try...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.40,0:25:14.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那块玻璃砖\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the glass brick,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.40,0:25:20.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来自于他那段被戴维所束缚时间的那个纪念品\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the souvenir of his years of bondage to Davy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.75,0:25:35.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}见效了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It did the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.22,0:25:36.99,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}磁场的能量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The force of the magnet
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.02,0:25:38.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}使光线产生了扭曲\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}twisted the light
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.76,0:25:41.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从而穿越了水晶\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}so that it could pass through the crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.36,0:25:43.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 这当中有什么重大意义呢\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, what's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.73,0:25:45.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉第揭示了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday had demonstrated the existence
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.00,0:25:48.60,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们身边存在的物理现实\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the physical reality that surrounds us,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.60,0:25:51.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是前人所不知道的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but which no one had ever been able to detect.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.41,0:25:53.41,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是一个激动人心的时刻\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It was as dramatic a breakthrough
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.44,0:25:56.18,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}犹如人类第一次\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as seeing the cosmos for the very first time
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.21,0:25:57.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}通过望远镜看到宇宙\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}through a telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.61,0:26:01.25,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}通过展示电磁力\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By showing that an electromagnetic force
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.28,0:26:03.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以操纵光线\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}could manipulate light,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.12,0:26:06.52,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉弟发现了自然界深层存在的一种力的联结\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday had discovered a deeper unity of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.55,0:26:09.09,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他为爱因斯坦打开了一道大门\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He had opened a door for Einstein
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.12,0:26:11.69,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也为后世的物理学家开创了新的天地\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and all the physicists who came after him
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.73,0:26:13.49,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让人类可以窥见\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to glimpse the interplay
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.53,0:26:16.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇宙深处中最基本的隐秘力量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of hidden, primal forces in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.76,0:26:19.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使是在达到他的天才的顶峰之时\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Even as he approached the summit of his genius,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.87,0:26:22.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他还在为抑郁症所困扰\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he was plagued by depression
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.04,0:26:23.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直在怀疑自己的能力\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and doubts about his ability
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.74,0:26:26.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能不能记住最简单的问题\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to retain even the simplest thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.07,0:26:30.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朋友们 我发现我很难回答\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}My dear friend, I find a difficulty in answering
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.11,0:26:33.05,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或是正确地了解科学论文的内容\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or even acknowledging properly a scientific letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.08,0:26:36.22,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我记不住东西\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for I cannot now hold it at once in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.25,0:26:39.49,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有一部分记忆力不行了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The memory of the parts fail me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.26,0:26:44.69,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有 很遗憾你会看到\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}P.S. You will be sorry to see
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.73,0:26:46.59,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}后面这段提示的话\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the tone of this short note,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.63,0:26:50.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我亲爱的老公已经和平时不一样了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but my dearest husband is not quite so well as usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.50,0:26:53.03,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望他能变好吧\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but I hope he will improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.07,0:26:56.07,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真诚的莎拉・法拉弟\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yours very truly, S. Faraday.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.17,0:27:01.57,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}年轻时 法拉弟自贫困中崛起\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}As a young man, Faraday had risen from poverty,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.61,0:27:04.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在一个对出身阶级非常注重的社会中成长\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in one of the most class-conscious societies
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.08,0:27:06.41,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是当时世界上阶级划分最严格的社会\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the world has ever known,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.45,0:27:10.32,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并成为当时最负盛名的科学家\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to become the most celebrated scientist of his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.35,0:27:13.92,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}40岁的时候 他发明了电动马达\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By age 40, he had invented the electric motor,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.95,0:27:16.62,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}变压器 发电机\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the transformer, the generator,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.66,0:27:19.66,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些设备改变了家庭\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}machines that would change everything about the home,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.69,0:27:22.10,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}农场 工厂里的一切\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the farm, the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.13,0:27:25.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在 在60岁的时候 在这位伟大的物理学家\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, at 60, decades after the fertile periods
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.80,0:27:28.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}作出一系列巨大发现后的几十年\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the greatest physicists,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.04,0:27:30.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他被失忆和抑郁所困扰\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}plagued by memory loss and melancholy,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.84,0:27:33.91,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但他无畏地继续深入探索\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he fearlessly probed deeper
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.94,0:27:37.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那看不见的神秘力量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}into the mysterious invisible forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.75,0:27:58.79,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在世人认为法拉弟已经过时的时候\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The world thought that Michael Faraday was a has-been.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.82,0:28:00.72,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他无视忧郁症\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Despite his depression,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.76,0:28:04.06,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一如既往地充满好奇心\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he remained as passionately curious as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.10,0:28:05.63,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在发现了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Having discovered the unity
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.66,0:28:08.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电 磁 光三者的有机联系之后\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of electricity, magnetism and light,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.17,0:28:09.97,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}法拉弟想要知道自然界中这三者的能量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Faraday needed to know
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.00,0:28:13.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是如何合而为一 共同发挥作用的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}how this trinity of natural forces work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.14,0:28:21.44,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歌词：这就是小姐走过的路\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}? this is the way the ladies walk... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.48,0:28:23.05,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实也没有什么新鲜的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This was nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.08,0:28:24.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩子们早已\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Children had been playing with magnets
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.68,0:28:26.62,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把磁铁与铁屑混在一起玩了好几个世纪了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and iron filings for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.65,0:28:30.22,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人们一直都认为那些好玩的图案\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Everyone had always assumed that this lovely pattern
